### Special Patterns

#### Overlay Action Button Padding
When using absolutely positioned overlay buttons (like three dots menu):
- Add `pr-12` (or matching button width) to content containers
- Prevents text overlap with overlay buttons
- Example: title rows with action menus

#### Section Anchor Offset
For anchor sections with fixed headers:
- Add `section-anchor` class to anchor sections
- Ensures correct scroll position on both desktop and mobile
- Used in welcome.html and pages with fixed headers

## Color System

### Primary Colors
- Primary: `#38bdf8` (blue)
- Background: `#0f172a` (dark blue)
- Card background: `rgba(30,41,59,0.85)`
- Border: `#232946`, `#334155`

### Text Colors
- Main text: `text-main`
- Muted text: `text-muted`
- Chip text: `text-chip`

### Background Colors
- Input: `bg-input`
- Chip: `bg-chip`
- Card hover: `bg-card-hover`

## Layout Guidelines

### Containers
- Use `max-w-4xl mx-auto` for main content containers
- Use `p-8` for main page padding
- Use `px-4` for responsive horizontal padding

### Spacing
- Use Tailwind spacing scale consistently
- Common patterns: `gap-4`, `mb-8`, `p-6`, `py-3`

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Use responsive prefixes (`sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`) when needed
- Test on both desktop and mobile

